abstract: Erik Jones wins Nascar Xfinity Series AttiCat 300 auto race.
lead_paragraph: Erik Jones took the lead from Ryan Blaney with 11 laps remaining and held on to win the Nascar Xfinity Series AttiCat 300.

headline.main: Erik Jones, 19, Completes Weekend Sweep With Win at AttiCat 300
